== Suggested Roles==
The Toukon is thoroughly middle-of-the-road as far as TMs go, except for above-average shielding.  However, it is outclassed in almost every respect by the [[Zephyrus|OTAS Zephyrus]]. In addition, it is only available from the shipyard at [[The Moon]], making the ship difficult to equip and deploy quickly. Still, the ship is as useful as any other TM if you should acquire one.

